               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">MR. BOTTOMLEY</hi> 
                  <hi rend="italic">conducted the Presecution.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18701121-name-133" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18701121-name-133" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18701121-name-133" type="surname" value="STANBURY"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18701121-name-133" type="given" value="JOHN"></interp>JOHN STANBURY</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a draper, at 238, Edgware Road—on the evening of the 1st November I was in Little Moorfields, going to the Metropolitan Station—I met the prisoner, and as he passed me he jumped at my watch, snapped the chain, and ran off with it—I pursued him very closely—I saw a man stop him—this is my watch (<hi rend="italic">produced.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18701121-name-134" type="witnessName">
                        <interp inst="t18701121-name-134" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18701121-name-134" type="surname" value="PURDON"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18701121-name-134" type="given" value="ALBERT"></interp>ALBERT PURDON</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a porter, in the employment of Mr. Wyman, of Fore Street—on the 1st November I was in Moor Lave, shutting a shop up—I beard a cry of "Stop thief!"—I saw the prisoner run round the corner into Moor Lane—I gave chase and caught him close to the police-station opposite Vine Court—he said "I am running after the thief—I said "Very well, if you are not the thief you have nothing to fear; you had better stop till they come up; "he said "Will you let me go I"—I said "No"—we had a struggle—I pulled him towards the station—the prosecutor came up and said "That is the man that has got my watch," and he guts him in custody.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18701121-name-135" type="witnessName">
