                        <interp inst="t18701121-name-135" type="surname" value="CULLINGWORTH"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18701121-name-135" type="given" value="RICHARD"></interp>RICHARD CULLINGWORTH</persName>
                  </hi> (<hi rend="italic">City Policeman</hi> 160). About 10 o'clock on the night of 1st November I found this watch a few yards up Vine Court, where the prisoner had passed just before he was stopped—I found the how of the watch down one grating and part of the chain down another.</p>
